snippet.title: Pahalgam Attack | Pahalgam Hero Who Carried Injured Boy On His Back: 'Humanity Before Religion'
snippet.description:
The massive terror attack in Pahalgam, Jammu and Kashmir, while spreading shock and horror, also showed hope as multiple heroes stepped forward from among the locals. One such was Sajad Ahmed Bhatt. A video of him carrying a boy, injured when the terrorists opened fire on a group of tourists, killing 26 people, has been widely circulated. The video shows Mr Bhatt running downhill over the rocky terrain, his steps never faltering. The boy was on his back, clad in Mr Bhatt's orange jacket to keep him warm.

snippet.title: Phulera Ka Panchayati Raj | Alhua Vikas ft. Neena Gupta, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Durgesh Kumar
snippet.description:
Phulera mein banne wala hain Bhandaar Ghar par kya har baar ki tarah iss baar bhi Banrakas ko hogi Pradhan ji ke iss kaam se dikkat? Ab Phulera mein hoga vikas ya Banrakas ek baar phir kahega alhua vikas? Jaanne ke liye Rashtriya Panchayati Raj Diwas par dekhiye Phulera Ka Panchayati Raj.

#TVF #Phulera #PanchayatiRaj 

Watch all parts of #PhuleraKaPanchayatiRaj here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTB0eCoUXErY5Jgt1VEjySYTaPde_w5oG&si=pwoMUSOFjMWWbkHS

This film, released on the occasion of National Panchayati Raj Day (‡§∞‡§æ‡§∑‡•ç‡§ü‡•ç‡§∞‡•Ä‡§Ø ‡§™‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ‡§Ø‡§§‡•Ä ‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú ‡§¶‡§ø‡§µ‡§∏; 24th April, 2025), highlights the importance of Own Sources of Revenue (OSR) in enabling Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) to become self-reliant and better equipped to take up development works on their own.  It encourages Panchayats to adopt simple and effective ways to raise awareness among citizens about timely payment of Property Tax and other local taxes. These contributions directly support better service delivery, creation of public assets, and overall village development ‚Äì making citizens active partners in the progress of their communities.  With the central message ‚Äú‡§ú‡§Æ‡§æ ‡§ï‡§∞‡§ï‡•á ‡§ï‡§∞, ‡§¨‡§®‡§æ‡§à‡§Ø‡•á ‡§Ö‡§™‡§®‡•Ä ‡§™‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ‡§Ø‡§§ ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§Ü‡§§‡•ç‡§Æ‡§®‡§ø‡§∞‡•ç‡§≠‡§∞‚Äù, the film inspires collective efforts towards strengthening grassroots governance. The Ministry of Panchayati Raj remains committed to promoting OSR enhancement as a means to deepen decentralization and participatory rural development.

The Ministry of Panchayati Raj (MoPR), Government of India, is responsible for overseeing all matters related to Panchayati Raj and Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) across the country. MoPR plays a pivotal role in promoting the decentralization process and strengthening rural local governance in States and Union Territories. For more information, visit the Ministry's official website: https://panchayat.gov.in

With the central message ‚Äú‡§ú‡§Æ‡§æ ‡§ï‡§∞‡§ï‡•á ‡§ï‡§∞, ‡§¨‡§®‡§æ‡§à‡§Ø‡•á ‡§Ö‡§™‡§®‡•Ä ‡§™‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ‡§Ø‡§§ ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§Ü‡§§‡•ç‡§Æ‡§®‡§ø‡§∞‡•ç‡§≠‡§∞‚Äù, the film inspires collective efforts towards strengthening grassroots governance. The Ministry of Panchayati Raj remains committed to promoting OSR enhancement as a means to deepen decentralization and participatory rural development.

The Ministry of Panchayati Raj (MoPR), Government of India, is responsible for overseeing all matters related to Panchayati Raj and Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) across the country. MoPR plays a pivotal role in promoting the decentralization process and strengthening rural local governance in States and Union Territories. For more information, visit the Ministry's official website: https://panchayat.gov.in

snippet.title: #NC24 - The Excavation Begins | Naga Chaitanya | Karthik Dandu | Sukumar | Ajaneesh Loknath | SVCC
snippet.description:
NC24 - The Excavation Begins on Sri Venkateswara Cine Chitra.

Welcome to the world of NC24, an upcoming mythical thriller Starring Yuvasamrat Naga Chaitanya in a never-before-seen avatar. Directed by visionary filmmaker Karthik Dandu, Produced by BVSN Prasad and Sukumar under the prestigious banners of Sri Venkateswara Cine Chitra and Sukumar Writings.

Cinematography by the talented Neil D'Cunha, Music by the hauntingly brilliant B. Ajaneesh Loknath, Editing by National Award-winning editor Naveen Nooli with Production Design by master visual craftsman Sri Nagendra Tangala.

snippet.description:
Ray is reeling from disappointment after losing the project lead opportunity at work ‚Äî and to make it worse, it went to the new guy, Abhinav. Struggling to focus, keep up with deadlines, and stay emotionally afloat, she starts to question her worth at the office.

Meanwhile, Nikhat is on a mission of her own: to finally make a move on Abeer. With Manav‚Äôs less-than-helpful guidance, things go sideways fast ‚Äî and hilariously. From romantic misfires to workplace pressure, Adulting Season 3 continues to explore the chaos of ambition, heartbreak, and growing pains in your 20s.

Starring Aisha Ahmed, Yashaswini Dayama, Viraj Ghelani, and Rohan Khurana, Episode 2 brings more warmth, awkward laughs, and too-real emotions as Ray and Nikhat juggle friendship, failure, and flirtations ‚Äî all while trying to keep it together in the middle of Mumbai.

Mann Mast Malang Digitally Presented by Diamond Paints - Ujooba Beauty Cream & Nestle Lactogrow

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fianc√©s turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.title: Chor Bazari Phir Se | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar, Wamiqa | Tanishk, Pritam, Irshad, Neeraj, Sunidhi
snippet.description:
Chor bazaari do nainon kee,
Pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi!

Presenting the highly awaited ‚ÄòChor Bazari Phir Se‚Äô from ‚ÄòBhool Chuk Maaf‚Äô, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Wamiqa Gabbi! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Pritam, it is sung by Neeraj Shridhar, Sunidhi Chauhan, Zahrah S Khan and Tanishk Bagchi. Penned by Irshad Kamil, it is perfect for all the Bollywood nostalgia lovers and those who love a good beat to dance on. Play it on loop, add it to your playlists, and get your groove on with ‚ÄòChor Bazari Phir Se‚Äô!

#ChorBazari #PhirSe #RajkummarRao #WamiqaGabbi #TanishkBagchi #Pritam #IrshadKamil #NeerajShridhar #SunidhiChauhan #ZahrahSKhan #BhoolChukMaaf 

Title: Chor Bazari Phir Se
Singer: Neeraj Shridhar, Sunidhi Chauhan, Zahrah S Khan and Tanishk Bagchi 
Composers: Tanishk Bagchi and Pritam 
Music Production: Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil
Language: Hindi
Mix Master: Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai
Original Music: Pritam
Director of Photography- Manu Anand
Director of Choreography- Vijay A Ganguly 
Costume Designer - Sheetal Iqbal Sharma 

Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast - Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan 
Directed By: Karan Sharma 
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota 
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi 
Background Score: Ketan Sodha 
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma 
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee 
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil
Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
Associate Producer: Vineeta S Tanwar

Lyrics:
Chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi 
Pyaar kee jo teri-meri umr aayi thi vo katt gayi
Tu bhi tu hai main bhi main hoon duniyaan saaree dekh ulat gayi
Tu naa jaane main naa jaanoon kaise saaree baath palat gayi
Ghatni hi thi ye bhi ghatana ghatate-ghatate lo ye ghat gai
Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi

Jhoomariya jhoomariya manwa
Ban baagi sa
Jhoomariya jhoomariya tanwa
Bedaagi
Man mera dhad dhad dhad dhadkaaye
Koi na phir sar sar sar chadh jaaye
Kasam se baazi haath na apne aaye
Nain agar lad jaayein

Taareef teri karnaa tuje khone se darana
Haan bhool gaya ab tujh pe din mein chaar dafa maranaa

Taareef teri karnaa tuje khone se darana
Haan bhool gaya ab tujh pe din mein chaar dafa maranaa

Laaj-sharam kee choti-moti jo thi dori vo bhi katt gayi
Chowk-chaubaare gali-mohalle khol ke main saare ghunghat gayi
Ek hue the do se donon donon kee ab raahen bant gayi
Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi

Bade hi nain ladaake se
Lade the roz baazaaron mein
Kisi ko dhoond hi lete the
Sadak pe roz hazaaron mein
Bahas nahin kam kam kam karte
Na ab yeh gham gham gham karte
Badal gaye dheere dheere do naina
Mera kya kya kya kehna

Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi
Haan rang-birangaa paani pee ke sidhi-saadi kudi bighad gayi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The director of Prey welcomes you to a world of hurt. Experience Predator: Badlands on the big screen, in theaters and IMAX November 7.
 
‚ÄúPredator: Badlands,‚Äù which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator (Schuster-Koloamatangi), outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O‚ÄôConnor.

snippet.title: Adulting | S3E01 - Pawri Ho Rahi Hai | Ft. Aisha & Yashaswini | Dice Media | Web Series
snippet.description:
Nikhat is back from Hyderabad and determined to make Ray‚Äôs 25th birthday unforgettable. Balloons, plans, surprises ‚Äî she‚Äôs ready to go all out. But there‚Äôs just one problem: Ray doesn‚Äôt want to celebrate.

She‚Äôs got her eyes on something bigger ‚Äî a life-changing project lead announcement at work the very next day. The last thing she wants is a hangover or distractions. But can birthdays be ignored? And more importantly, can best friends ever be on the same page when life pulls them in opposite directions?

Adulting Season 3 opens with all the emotional confusion, hilarious miscommunication, and ride-or-die friendship moments you‚Äôve loved since Season 1. From navigating work anxiety to the pressure of turning 25, Episode 1 brings back the Mumbai madness, the career chaos, and the comfort of chosen family ‚Äî one heartfelt moment at a time.

üë≠ Starring Aisha Ahmed and Yashaswini Dayama, & Viraj Ghelani, Adulting S3 dives deeper into the realities of millennial friendships, workplace hustle, and the little moments that define adulthood.

en-IN.description:
Nikhat is back from Hyderabad and determined to make Ray‚Äôs 25th birthday unforgettable. Balloons, plans, surprises ‚Äî she‚Äôs ready to go all out. But there‚Äôs just one problem: Ray doesn‚Äôt want to celebrate.

She‚Äôs got her eyes on something bigger ‚Äî a life-changing project lead announcement at work the very next day. The last thing she wants is a hangover or distractions. But can birthdays be ignored? And more importantly, can best friends ever be on the same page when life pulls them in opposite directions?

Adulting Season 3 opens with all the emotional confusion, hilarious miscommunication, and ride-or-die friendship moments you‚Äôve loved since Season 1. From navigating work anxiety to the pressure of turning 25, Episode 1 brings back the Mumbai madness, the career chaos, and the comfort of chosen family ‚Äî one heartfelt moment at a time.

üë≠ Starring Aisha Ahmed and Yashaswini Dayama, & Viraj Ghelani, Adulting S3 dives deeper into the realities of millennial friendships, workplace hustle, and the little moments that define adulthood.
